Using 3rd Party Modules

type in node.js cmd:

    npm - v                                 (to find npm version)
    npm init                                (survey projects)
    ctl + c  ---> ^C                        (to quit)
    
- searches
    npmjs.com
    -s: lodash                              (makes dev node.js & js hella easier)
    
    node install (< lodash >) --save        (install and saves to update)
    node install                            (once the package has been installed and deleted. can be reinstalled.)